## 5) 🔌 API Contract

### Base conventions (existing)

```json
// Success
{ "success": true, "data": { ... } }
// Error
{ "success": false, "error_code": "SOME_CODE", "message": "Human readable" }
```

### Endpoints

---

#### 5.1 Material Request — Create

> Already exists but documented here for completeness.

```
POST /material-requests
Auth: JWT (role: production)
```

```json
// Request
{
  "model_id": "uuid",
  "cost_center_id": "uuid",
  "process_name": "Assembly",
  "remarks": "Urgent restock",
  "items": [
    {
      "part_number": "PIN430-A-001",
      "description": "Pin 430 component",
      "requested_qty": 500,
      "uom": "PCS"
    }
  ]
}
// Response 201
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "id": "uuid",
    "request_no": "MR-20260302-0001",
    "dmi_no": "DMI-20260302-0001",
    "status": "REQUESTED"
  }
}
```

---

#### 5.2 Material Request — Approve / Reject

```
POST /material-requests/:id/approve
POST /material-requests/:id/reject
Auth: JWT (role per workflow_approval_configs)
```

```json
// Approve — no body required (remarks optional)
{ "remarks": "OK" }

// Reject — remarks required
{ "remarks": "Wrong model, please re-submit" }

// Response 200
{ "success": true, "data": { "id": "uuid", "status": "APPROVED" } }
```

---

#### 5.3 Store Issue — Confirm (creates handover batch)

> Extends existing issue endpoint. After issuing, auto-create handover batch.

```
POST /material-requests/:id/issue
Auth: JWT (role: store)
```

```json
// Request (existing allocations payload)
{
  "dmi_no": "DMI-20260302-0001",
  "remarks": "Issued from Rack B",
  "allocations": [
    {
      "item_id": "uuid",
      "part_number": "PIN430-A-001",
      "do_number": "DO-2026-001",
      "issued_packs": 5,
      "issued_qty": 500,
      "vendor_pack_size": 100
    }
  ]
}

// Response 200  (extended with handover info)
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "id": "uuid",
    "status": "ISSUED",
    "handover_batch": {
      "id": "uuid",
      "batch_no": "HB-20260302-0001",
      "status": "PENDING",
      "expected_item_count": 5
    }
  }
}
```

**Server-side effect**: Creates `handover_batches` + `handover_batch_items` from the allocations.

