│  │  8   │ PIN430-001 │ L26-B  │ DUPLICAT │ 10:24:55       │ │
│  │  7   │ PIN300-001 │ L26-A  │ MATCHED  │ 10:24:48       │ │
│  └──────┴────────────┴────────┴──────────┴────────────────┘ │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**UX rules for scanning speed**:

| Rule | Implementation |
|------|----------------|
| Auto-focus scan input | `useEffect` → `inputRef.current.focus()` on mount and after every scan result |
| Auto-submit on Enter | `onKeyDown` handler, submit immediately (no "Scan" button needed) |
| Clear input after scan | After API response arrives, clear input field and re-focus |
| Status toast auto-clear | `MessageStrip` with 3-second timeout for success, 5-second for errors |
| Audio feedback | Play success/error beep sounds via `Audio API` (optional, configurable) |
| No page navigation mid-scan | Single-page experience; scanned items table updates in-place |
| Finalize button disabled until ≥1 scan | Prevent accidental empty finalize |
| Keyboard-only operation | Tab order: scan input → finalize button. No mouse required. |

**UI5 Components used**: `Bar`, `Input`, `MessageStrip`, `AnalyticalTable`, `Panel`, `Button`, `ObjectStatus`, `FlexBox`, `NumericContent` (via cards), `Dialog` (for finalize confirmation).

